Comment: This game is one I thought I played fairly well. It is good to have luck on your side also. Kings Opening. I am especially weak playing as black. Partially because the guy that got me into playing chess always let me start the games as white. I played probably 300 games as white before I ever played a game as black. Feel free to comment or point out a move I missed or even how lucky I was this game.
